flowchart TD
    Start([Customer wants meal-prep]) --> Plans[Browse subscription plans]
    Plans --> Pick[Choose plan:<br/>meal type, price, billing interval]
    Pick --> Sched[Choose delivery schedule<br/>+ delivery address]
    Sched --> AuthGate{Logged in?}
    AuthGate -- No --> Login[Login or register] --> Setup
    AuthGate -- Yes --> Setup

    Setup[Create subscription via Stripe/Cashier] --> FirstPay{First charge ok?}
    FirstPay -- Failed --> PayFail[Show error] --> Pick
    FirstPay -- Success --> Active[Subscription = Active<br/>set next_delivery_date]
    Active --> NotiA[Confirmation notification]

    NotiA --> Cycle{{Recurring cycle - scheduled job}}
    Cycle --> Bill[Cashier charges next cycle]
    Bill --> BillRes{Charge result}
    BillRes -- Success --> Record[Write subscription_payment<br/>generate delivery] --> Renew[Renewal notification] --> Cycle
    BillRes -- Failed --> Retry[Dunning: retry / notify customer]
    Retry --> Resolved{Resolved?}
    Resolved -- Yes --> Record
    Resolved -- No --> PastDue[Mark past due / pause] --> Manage

    Active --> Manage[Manage subscription]
    Manage --> M1[Pause: stop billing & deliveries]
    Manage --> M2[Resume: reactivate + reschedule]
    Manage --> M3[Cancel: stop future cycles]
    Manage --> M4[View history & status]
    M1 --> Paused([Paused])
    Paused --> M2
    M2 --> Active
    M3 --> Cancelled([Cancelled - no future billing])
